  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Aaritz is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Fuel up for the day at the varied buffet breakfast including hot and cold options. Each evening you can enjoy four courses with a mix of international and South Tyrolean dishes, along with a generous salad buffet. </p>
<p>There's a weekly gala evening with cocktails and Christmas and New Year's Eve gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Aaritz has an unbeatable location right in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> directly opposite the Ciampinoi gondola. We love the elegance of this hotel - a grand staircase leads down to the lounge with a log-burning fireplace and comfy sofas. The rooms are beautifully decorated and they all come with a balcony and views over the valley or the village. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>You couldn't ask for a better location. Set on the main high street of Selva, the Ciamponoi gondola station is just opposite the hotel so you can easily get onto the fabulous <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomiti Ski Area</a>. If you are wanting to ski the clockwise circuit of the Sella Ronda, the Costabella chairlift is around a five minute walk which takes you to the Dantercepies run - from here you have access to the lovely red run heading back towards Selva or can drop down into <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Colfsco and Covara</a>. </p>
<h2>Unwind and relax </h2>
<p>After a strenuous day of skiing, make the most of the wellness area - have a dip in the pool, unwind in the steam bath or have a moment of peace in one of the saunas. For a local fee, book a massage or treatment to thoroughly revitalise. If you are wanting to stay active, even off the slopes, there is also a fitness room with a range of equipment. </p>
<p>Enjoy a drink or two in the lovely lounge area, with plenty of seating, and a generous fireplace, it is the perfect spot to catch up with friends and family. </p>]]></description>
